## ⚔️ FPS / RTS Hybrid System

### The Switch
- **FPS Mode** — First person, on foot or piloting a ship/vehicle
- **RTS Mode** — Camera pulls up to overhead view of active cell/sector
- Switch is seamless, no menus, no load — like Bannerlord on a battlefield

### What Each Mode Does
| Mode | Controls | Best For |
|------|----------|----------|
| FPS | Direct player control | Exploration, looting POIs, dogfighting |
| RTS | Command units on map | Large battles, base building, fleet management |

### Rules
- RTS view is bounded by the active planet cell or space sector
- Units follow orders while you're in FPS — AI executes your last command
- You can re-enter FPS as any unit you control (your character or a ship)

