## 🔧 Tech Stack
> **TBD — Decision pending (Phase 1)**

Candidates to evaluate:
- Unreal Engine 5 (best visuals, large world streaming built in)
- Unity (large asset ecosystem, more solo-dev friendly)
- Godot (open source, lightweight, growing ecosystem)

Key requirements from tech stack:
- Large world streaming support
- Seamless scene transitions (space ↔ planet)
- Strong physics for ships and on-foot
- Multiplayer capability (future phase)

